---
description: Documentation reading order and source-of-truth enforcement
alwaysApply: true
---

Before implementation:
1. Read `docs/README.md`.
2. Identify canonical source-of-truth docs for the task.
3. Treat `docs/archive/*` and `docs/rag_debug/*` as non-canonical context.

When behavior contracts change:
- Update canonical docs in the same change.
- Keep ADR references aligned in `docs/12_architecture_decisions.md` when new ADRs are added.

Language policy for engineering artifacts:
- English only in docs, rules, comments, and developer-facing notes.
- Do not introduce Cyrillic in engineering artifacts.
